       <h4>
        Spotlight on Scholarship in the Arts
       </h4>
       <p>
        Congratulations to winners of the 4 minutes, 33 seconds arts research competition! Kuo Zhang, Ph.D. candidate in the language and literacy education program won the presentation category, and posters winners (l-r) are Rhia Morena, Samantha Lynn Hudson and Bridget Dooley, with emcee David Saltz.
       </p>
